INK INSIDE is a CO-OP action RPG based on a lost cartoon pilot! Play as Stick (Brian David Gilbert) an unfinished doodle fighting back against the wet "Sog" corrupting the notebook they live in. Team up with a friend in CO-OP to find treasure, upgrade your characters, and beat-up the sog together!
